u.s. commerc secretari say export rise need commerc secretari malcolm baldrig said after the releas of a sharpli lower januari lead indic index that a pickup in export is need . `` the best tonic for the economi now would be a pickup in net export , '' he said in a statement after the depart report the index fell 1.0 pct in januari from decemb , the sharpest drop sinc a 1.7 pct fall in juli , 1984. the main reason for the januari declin after a 2.3 pct decemb rise were declin in build permit , new order for plant and equip and for consum and industri good .